title: Create the s16 chain
description: This corrects  the issues found in prop-8. This is a new proposal (prop-9) to create the consumer chain "s16-1". Visit https://github.com/s16rv/ics-testnets/tree/main/game-of-chains-2022/s16 and https://github.com/s16rv/s16 for details on this proposal's data and how to join the chain.
